@startuml
title Refund Request Lifecycle - 3.8 (RefundStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> PENDING : Customer requests refund /\nsystem queues mandatory refund
PENDING --> PROCESSING : Staff takes the request\n(PATCH /api/staff/refunds/:id)
PROCESSING --> APPROVED : Approved +\ngateway refund success
PROCESSING --> REJECTED : Staff rejects (+ reason,\nnon-mandatory only)
APPROVED --> [*]
REJECTED --> [*]

note right of PROCESSING
  Mandatory refunds
  cannot be rejected
end note
@enduml
